function CopyImage% CopyImage(image)% % Copy the matrix "image" to the clipboard in PICT format. Use this to% pass image data from Matlab to other programs. Image data should be% in the range 0 to 255. A grayscale image should have size MxN. An% RGB image should have size MxNx3.%% Images are handled in the same way as in Screen 'PutImage'.% % Also see PasteImage, SaveAsEps, and Screen 'SaveAsEps'.% 8/19/94		dhb		Link in new pixmap handling code.% 5/22/02		dgp		Rewritten to be compatible with Screen PutImage.